reviewText: Since it is a product from Europe it isn't compatible with any of my devices in the US. I cant seem to get the dvds to play on anything I own. Very disappointing..
I bought this and it wouldn't play on my DVD player or in my computer MP3 everything says the file is not recognized cost too much money to send it back so it was thrown away
Do not buy these!  None of the DVDs will play!  Save your money and time.
Does not play on a DVD or blue ray player or even a laptop , something wrong with the discs
